```mermaid.flowchart
flowchart TD
    Start([User Request]) --> Orchestrator[ORCHESTRATOR]

    Orchestrator --> Parse[1. Parse Request<br/>Làm sạch & chuẩn hóa]
    Parse --> Complexity[2. Complexity Analyzer<br/>Phân tích độ phức tạp]
    Complexity --> Decision{Đơn giản?}

    %% Simple Path
    Decision -->|Yes| DirectLLM[3. Direct LLM<br/>Trả lời trực tiếp]
    DirectLLM --> FormatSimple[4. Format Response]
    FormatSimple --> Response([Response])

    %% Complex Path - Research Only
    Decision -->|No| Planning[3. Planning Agent<br/>Tạo Research Plan<br/>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━<br/>Tool: 🔍 Research Tool]
    Planning --> ExecuteLoop[4. Execute Research Tasks<br/>Thực thi tuần tự]
    ExecuteLoop --> Research[🔍 Research Task <br/>Web Search + Extract Info]
    Research --> Collect[5. Aggregate Results<br/>Tổng hợp tất cả kết quả research]
    Collect --> FormatComplex[6. Compose Response<br/>LLM viết lại response từ research data]
    FormatComplex --> Response

    %% Styling (đã loại tone vàng/cam)
    style Orchestrator fill:#FCE4EC,stroke:#E91E63,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Complexity fill:#E3F2FD,stroke:#1976D2,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Decision fill:#E5F9FF,stroke:#00BCD4,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style DirectLLM fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#4CAF50,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Planning fill:#E8EAF6,stroke:#5C6BC0,stroke-width:4px,color:#000
    style ExecuteLoop fill:#E1F5FE,stroke:#03A9F4,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Research fill:#E0F7FA,stroke:#00ACC1,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Collect fill:#EDE7F6,stroke:#7E57C2,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style FormatComplex fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#AB47BC,stroke-width:3px,color:#000
    style Start fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#66BB6A,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style Response fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#66BB6A,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    style FormatSimple fill:#F3E5F5,stroke:#AB47BC,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
```